<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>แก้ไขผู้ใช้</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Prompt',sans-serif;
}

body{
margin:0;
background:#f4f6f9;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
height:100vh;
}

/* Card */

.card{
background:#fff;
padding:35px;
border-radius:14px;
width:420px;
box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

/* Header */

.header{
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.header h2{
margin:0;
font-size:22px;
color:#111827;
}

.header p{
margin:4px 0 0;
font-size:13px;
color:#6b7280;
}

/* Form */

.form-group{
margin-bottom:16px;
}

label{
display:block;
font-size:14px;
margin-bottom:6px;
font-weight:500;
}

input,select{
width:100%;
padding:10px 12px;
border:1px solid #e5e7eb;
border-radius:8px;
font-size:14px;
outline:none;
transition:0.2s;
}

input:focus,select:focus{
border-color:#3b82f6;
box-shadow:0 0 0 2px rgba(59,130,246,.15);
}

/* Buttons */

.btn-group{
display:flex;
gap:10px;
margin-top:20px;
}

.btn{
flex:1;
padding:10px;
border:none;
border-radius:8px;
font-size:14px;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.2s;
}

.save{
background:#3b82f6;
color:#fff;
}

.save:hover{
background:#2563eb;
}

.back{
background:#6b7280;
color:#fff;
}

.back:hover{
background:#4b5563;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card">

<div class="header">
<h2>✏️ แก้ไขข้อมูลผู้ใช้</h2>
<p>แก้ไขข้อมูลของผู้สูงอายุหรืออาสาในระบบ</p>
</div>

<form method="POST">

<div class="form-group">
<label>ชื่อผู้ใช้</label>
<input type="text" name="name" value="<%= user.name %>" required>
</div>

<div class="form-group">
<label>ประเภทผู้ใช้</label>
<select name="role">
<option value="elder" <%= user.role=="elder"?"selected":"" %>>ผู้สูงอายุ</option>
<option value="volunteer" <%= user.role=="volunteer"?"selected":"" %>>อาสา</option>
</select>
</div>

<div class="form-group">
<label>สถานะการใช้งาน</label>
<select name="status">
<option value="approved" <%= user.status=="approved"?"selected":"" %>>อนุมัติ</option>
<option value="pending" <%= user.status=="pending"?"selected":"" %>>รออนุมัติ</option>
<option value="rejected" <%= user.status=="rejected"?"selected":"" %>>ปฏิเสธ</option>
</select>
</div>

<div class="btn-group">

<button type="submit" class="btn save">
💾 บันทึก
</button>

<a href="/admin/users" style="flex:1;">
<button type="button" class="btn back">
⬅ กลับ
</button>
</a>

</div>

</form>

</div>

</body>
</html>